{"tid":1465830,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［風向撚］和理非運動捉鬼0用處，請停止捉鬼","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:51.000Z","uid":183798,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d8dd4cc910be15ca9a49af10825d28be2826d9ac","tid":1465830,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:28.000Z","msg":"你話勇武捉鬼 以免煽動就話<br />\n<br />\n你依家捉呢啲咁既非警犬類鬼<br />\n其實好撚大機會係有身分人士特登比你地捉<br />\n唔撚係屈 係直接比個氹你踩<br />\n<br />\n和理非捉完鬼 又唔係打 又唔係除佢衫游街示眾<br />\n咁圍住佢做乜鳩呢 <br />\n<br />\n唔捉都捉左 其實盡快完事咪算 你又唔敢打 不如唔好捉 發現呢啲人咪大大聲講出黎 之後杯9佢算 （和理非活動）<br />\n<br />\n勇武活動你發現到佢係煽動既危險鬼 咪制服佢 打佢一身 <br />\n<br />\n再咁捉完又比人屈 搞到人心惶惶 運動會好快散 popo目的又達成"},{"pid":"377856c6152357616819cb3f876443a800c2ddb8","tid":1465830,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c429fafa32b7913b93f46fdef51fe1cb98ae353","tid":1465830,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:14.000Z","msg":"氣車推推"},{"pid":"d4a5cd5949dc37b7a66c7735737b80f5df612cee","tid":1465830,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c6840e69be26ebb32c10256cb9db8bb718a0fc","tid":1465830,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:50.000Z","msg":"嗰班人係警察扮示威者 煽動架 好明顯"},{"pid":"2eeead2ee7b71bd8359b4d95895d7b19cddb1f27","tid":1465830,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7390dbe3142704a561bfc656e1f59fbebcee6e99","tid":1465830,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:24:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db8a497cdeb3d5fe4afe35030fae2a81319fa8d8","tid":1465830,"uid":79278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5c6840e69be26ebb32c10256cb9db8bb718a0fc","tid":1465830,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc